Welcoming the new restrictions on junk-food advertising, 
@Matthew_RCSEng  said: " We now urge the Government to implement these proposals in full in the forthcoming Health and Care Bill."

https://t.co/AMnmVKC35Z

@PHE_uk have published a toolkit on #oralhealth for adults in #carehomes to support care homes and commissioners to implement @NICEComms guidance.

It also contains useful links for care home staff, residents, their families and friends. 

Read it online: https://t.co/OHeCCP53FX https://t.co/hj0NTYD0dc

The FDS supports some of the key asks included in 
@ObesityAPPG’s #PositionStatement and #PolicyWishList.

It is vital the Government takes action and implements the Childhood Obesity Plan and Prevention Green Paper, which include action on sugar levels in food and drink. https://t.co/L7RkocwdDv
